public interface NetworkedElement
extends NameTag

A representation of the model object 'Name Tagged Element'. Name tagged element with area, zone and owner arributes. It optionally holds a list of ref to CIM record. It has a sortNumber for storing sorting number. The intFlag is for storing some int for certain purpose, usually transient. visited attribute is for network walk through implementation

The following features are supported:

  • Visited
  • Weight
  • Int Flag
  • Sort Number
  • Area
  • Zone
  • Owner
  • Cim Rec
